],[404,"shone"],[405,"all"],[406,"night"],[407,"long,"],[408,"spreading"],[409,"her"],[410,"calm"],[411,"light"],[412,"all"],[413,"around."],[414,"And"],[415,"Tinku"],[416,"slept"],[417,"all"],[418,"through"],[419,"the"],[420,"night!"]]}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":420}}